{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961840/extras/howto01.gif?t=1724318873\" /><br>Shore Doodle: Drawing in the Sand is a drawing app that allows you to use your own personal beach as a canvas for your art.<br>There are no obstacles, no enemies obstructing you from your goal. So grab a branch or a rake and draw whatever you feel like in the sand!<br>Perfect for whenever you want a little moment to yourself, or if you want to recapture that summer feeling while you\u2019re hanging out at home.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961840/extras/howto02.gif?t=1724318873\" /><br>When night falls, the tide will come in and begin to wash away your drawings bit by bit, but that's part of the fun! Draw something and experience the unique comfort in knowing that it will not be forever.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2961840/extras/time.gif?t=1724318873\" /><br>While the app is running, the sky also changes based on how much time has passed. Try looking up as you draw to see it change from daytime, to sunset, to a starry night sky!<br>You might even see and hear a passing flock of birds! Seeing your surroundings change in real time is also part of the fun.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961840/5f9126f761734e529df191a62cde2d7fdbf65ac5.jpg"},{"name":"You're Back Again!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961840/532b1ab3ba2d560a2f75065657e79f2418b1e9a1.jpg"},{"name":"Have a nice play!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961840/e255b7592458807f8a89b94974f2fbc195cddffd.jpg"},{"name":"Challenger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2961840/9b312614e